## Block JSON Format

```json
{"opcode":"motion_movesteps","next":null,"parent":null,"inputs":{"STEPS":[1,[4,"10"]]},"fields":{},"shadow":false,"topLevel":true}
```

Inputs: `[1,[4,"10"]]`=number, `[1,[10,"text"]]`=string, `[1,[12,"id","name"]]`=variable, `[2,"blockId"]`=reporter.

## Coordinate System
Stage 480×360. x:[-240,240], y:[-180,180], center:(0,0). 0°=up, 90°=right.

## Python API Quick Ref
- `unpack_sb3(path)` / `pack_sb3(dir, path)` — file I/O
- `create_empty_project()`, `add_sprite()`, `create_block()` — low-level
- `ScratchProject` class — high-level builder
- `make_movesteps(n)`, `make_say(msg)`, `make_forever()`, etc. — block builders
- `validate_project(data)` → `(bool, issues)` — always validate before shipping

